      <title>大型科技股暴跌后，逢低买入者获利，股市回升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-16/big-tech-wipeout-turns-to-dip-buyer-bounty-as-stocks-surge-back</link>
